line_1: Still gaz'd, and listen'd: then her name besought:
line_2: Her winning voice the youth attentive caught:
For wrong to generous William wrought;

line_1: His soul enrapt; yet courteous then besought
line_2: Replete with kind and hospitable thought,

line_1: His soul enrapt; yet courteous then besought
line_2: To a sequestered bower the wearied Psyche brought.

line_1: And him of gentlest courtesy besought
line_2: For this the FAIRY KNIGHT with anxious thought,
